For all you Chucky fans out there . . . enjoy :o)

Please seed this torrent to help others get these fab movies.

*Child's Play* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0094862/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0094862/&lt;/a&gt;
A serial killer mortally wounded by the police transfers his soul into a doll (Chucky) with the power of voodoo. He soon realises unless he gets his soul into another body soon, he will be trapped forever. He also seeks revenge on the man who set him up, and wants to take over the boys body. Lots of violence and carnage ensues . . .

*Child's Play 2* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099253/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0099253/&lt;/a&gt;
Chucky returns to persue Andy - the boy who's body he must take over if he is ever to get out of the dolls body. He is prepared to butcher and main anyone who gets in his way.

*Child's Play 3* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0103956/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0103956/&lt;/a&gt;
It's been eight years andt Andy has enrolled in military school. Following the bad publicity of it's 'Chucky' dolls, the production line resumes, and the serial killer is back and begins his search for Andy, who is the only one who knows what Chucky is up to, and it's now up to him to put a stop to it.

*Child's Play 4 - Bride of Chucky* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0144120/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0144120/&lt;/a&gt;
The serial killer is back! This time his girlfriend Tiffany has revived him, once again in the form of the popular &quot;Chucky&quot; doll. Shortly after the &quot;happy&quot; couple's reunion, Chucky kills her and brings her back in the form of a girl's bridal doll. The two then embark on a killing spree en route to dig up Ray's corpse, which was buried with a Satanic voodoo charm capable of bringing back the dead

*Child's Play 5 - Seed of Chucky* &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0387575/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0387575/&lt;/a&gt;
The orphan doll offspring of Chucky and Tiffany is here!. When production starts on a movie detailing the urban legend of his parents' lethal exploits, Glen heads for Hollywood where he brings his bloodthirsty parents back from the dead. The family dynamics are far from perfect as Chucky and Tiffany go Hollywood and get rolling on a new spree of murderous mayhem; much to gentle Glen's horror. Chucky can't believe that his child doesn't want to walk in his murdering footsteps, and star-struck Tiffany can't believe that the movie will star her favorite actress, Jennifer Tilly, who soon becomes an unwitting hostess to this new family in more ways than one.
